text: Jari Matti Lipponen is a retired archer from Finland. He was born on 17 October 1972. Lipponen competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics, 1996 Summer Olympics, and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Jari LipponenJari LIPPONEN == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Finland
